{
  "stem": "151.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was hardly any breathing space and hardly any breathing air because there was a bucket which was supposed to be our sanitary facility, our bathroom.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It kept overflowing and I don't have to tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Within a few hours, it just kept overflowing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The cattle cars were never opened to emptied or to get a lot of fresh air into the car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so the stench and the air was unbreathable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we could actually hear people suffocating in the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course there was nothing we could about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had no food or water given to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this journey lasted three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I also remember during the night the train used to stop and the Nazi's used to bang on the walls of the cattle car, telling us that if we are still hiding any valuables or any money we should give it up or we'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And while they were talking to us we could hear on the outside shooting and screaming and we were convinced that they are searching and killing these people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I very vividly remember this old woman who was sitting on the edge of the cattle car who ripped open her coat lining and reached in there and removed a little gold locket and started to cry.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Opened this locket and started to cry bitterly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I being young and still very optimistic and romantic, I was sort of fantasizing that maybe that's her wedding picture in the locket or maybe her family, her grandchildren, whom she left behind.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were going somewhere not knowing where for how long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The rumors were that we're going to Germany to work and if the family is healthy and strong, we'll work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The family will survive together.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
